8.0, 856.0], [741.0, 856.0]], [[710.0, 678.0], [737.0, 678.0], [737.0, 767.0], [710.0, 767.0]]], "lines": ["俺を触る手は", "まるでブランド品を", "扱うような", "汚らわしい手に", "見える。"]}, {"box": [305, 339, 429, 596], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24, "lines_coords": [[[403.0, 340.0], [429.0, 340.0], [426.0, 495.0], [399.0, 495.0]], [[370.0, 342.0], [396.0, 342.0], [396.0, 571.0], [370.0, 571.0]], [[334.0, 340.0], [360.0, 340.0], [360.0, 595.0], [334.0, 595.0]], [[307.0, 345.0], [324.0, 345.0], [324.0, 453.0], [307.0, 453.0]]], "lines": ["優しい言葉も", "俺の財布に向かって", "囁いているかのように", "聞こえる。"]}, {"box": [877, 1118, 1032, 1320], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[999.0, 1118.0], [1032.0, 1118.0], [1032.0, 1200.0], [999.0, 1200.0]], [[974.0, 1121.0], [996.0, 1121.0], [996.0, 1320.0], [974.0, 1320.0]], [[940.0, 1120.0], [968.0, 1120.0], [968.0, 1200.0], [940.0, 1200.0]], [[909.0, 1118.0], [935.0, 1118.0], [935.0, 1248.0], [909.0, 1248.0]], [[879.0, 1118.0], [902.0, 1118.0], [901.0, 1307.0], [877.0, 1307.0]]], "lines": ["角度は", "しっかり俺を見て", "いるが", "焦点が俺に", "定まっていない。"]}, {"box": [162, 1298, 343, 1500], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[318.0, 1303.0], [340.0, 1303.0], [340.0, 1425.0], [318.0, 1425.0]], [[284.0, 1298.0], [310.0, 1298.0], [307.0, 1428.0], [281.0, 1428.0]], [[253.0, 1301.0], [279.0, 1301.0], [279.0, 1453.0], [253.0, 1453.0]], [[223.0, 1300.0], [246.0, 1300.0], [245.0, 1500.0], [221.0, 1500.0]], [[190.0, 1300.0], [217.0, 1300.0], [217.0, 1450.0], [190.0, 1450.0]], [[162.0, 1301.0], [185.0, 1301.0], [185.0, 1375.0], [162.0, 1375.0]]], "lines": ["俺のずっと", "向こう側を", "見ているのか。", "俺のだいぶ手前を", "見ているのか", "．．．．．？"]}], "img_path": "132.png"}, {"version": "0.1.7", "img_width": 1102, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [717, 681, 817, 908], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[784.0, 681.0], [817.0, 681.0], [817.0, 826.0], [784.0, 826.0]], [[753.0, 684.0], [779.0, 684.0], [779.0, 907.0], [753.0, 907.0]], [[719.0, 681.0], [745.0, 681.0], [744.0, 879.0], [717.0, 879.0]]], "lines": ["俺の存在に", "気付いているのか", "さえ怪しい．．．"]}, {"box": [70, 1334, 167, 1475], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[139.0, 1335.0], [167.0, 1335.0], [167.0, 1446.0], [139.0, 1446.0]], [[101.0, 1334.0], [134.0, 1334.0], [134.0, 1451.0], [101.0, 1451.0]], [[70.0, 1335.0], [98.0, 1335.0], [98.0, 1475.0], [70.0, 1475.0]]], "lines": ["透明人間", "扱いしや", "がった．．．！"]}], "img_path": "133.png"}, {"version": "0.1.7", "img_width": 1100, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [906, 80, 993, 295], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24, "lines_coords": [[[971.0, 82.0], [993.0, 82.0], [993.0, 209.0], [971.0, 209.0]], [[937.0, 81.0], [964.0, 81.0], [964.0, 237.0], [937.0, 237.0]], [[906.0, 82.0], [928.0, 82.0], [928.0, 287.0], [906.0, 287.0]]], "lines": ["そうすると", "俺の見る目も", "疑惑に満ちてきて"]}, {"box": [207, 291, 297, 455], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[273.0, 295.0], [295.0, 295.0], [295.0, 420.0], [273.0, 420.0]], [[239.0, 292.0], [265.0, 292.0], [265.0, 421.0], [239.0, 421.0]], [[207.0, 292.0], [234.0, 292.0], [234.0, 454.0], [207.0, 454.0]]], "lines": ["俺から出る", "言葉も嘘に", "染まっていき、"]}, {"box": [909, 750, 998, 955], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[971.0, 750.0], [998.0, 750.0], [998.0, 881.0], [971.0, 881.0]], [[940.0, 750.0], [967.0, 750.0], [967.0, 929.0], [940.0, 929.0]], [[909.0, 750.0], [935.0, 750.0], [935.0, 954.0], [909.0, 954.0]]], "lines": ["自分にさえ", "嘘をつくように", "なっていった．．．"]}, {"box": [854, 1343, 973, 1545], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24, "lines_coords": [[[946.0, 1343.0], [973.0, 1343.0], [973.0, 1446.0], [946.0, 1446.0]], [[914.0, 1343.0], [940.0, 1343.0], [940.0, 1495.0], [914.0, 1495.0]], [[884.0, 1343.0], [906.0, 1343.0], [906.0, 1545.0], [884.0, 1545.0]], [[854.0, 1345.0], [876.0, 1345.0], [876.0, 1481.0], [854.0, 1481.0]]], "lines": ["そこには", "実感などなく", "もちろん自分など", "存在しない。"]}], "img_path": "134.png"}, {"version": "0.1.7", "img_width": 1101, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [768, 275, 921, 559], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[894.0, 276.0], [921.0, 276.0], [921.0, 432.0], [894.0, 432.0]], [[862.0, 275.0], [888.0, 275.0], [888.0, 482.0], [862.0, 482.0]], [[830.0, 275.0], [858.0, 275.0], [858.0, 407.0], [830.0, 407.0]], [[801.0, 278.0], [827.0, 278.0], [827.0, 559.0], [801.0, 559.0]], [[768.0, 276.0], [796.0, 276.0], [798.0, 390.0], [769.0, 390.0]]], "lines": ["俺はあわてて", "ニセモノの関心を", "集めていた", "金、モノ、マンションやら", "全て捨て、"]}, {"box": [65, 404, 163, 534], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31, "lines_coords": [[[131.0, 404.0], [163.0, 406.0], [159.0, 510.0], [126.0, 509.0]], [[101.0, 407.0], [128.0, 407.0], [128.0, 534.0], [101.0, 534.0]], [[65.0, 406.0], [99.0, 406.0], [99.0, 489.0], [65.0, 489.0]]], "lines": ["どこかへ", "逃げたかっ", "た．．．"]}, {"box": [768, 771, 890, 926], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[863.0, 775.0], [890.0, 775.0], [890.0, 878.0], [863.0, 878.0]], [[832.0, 773.0], [858.0, 773.0], [858.0, 926.0], [832.0, 926.0]], [[798.0, 771.0], [824.0, 771.0], [824.0, 878.0], [798.0, 878.0]], [[768.0, 773.0], [796.0, 773.0], [796.0, 862.0], [768.0, 862.0]]], "lines": ["ホテルと", "公園の狭間に", "きたわけ", "ですね。"]}, {"box": [109, 973, 137, 1078], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[109.0, 973.0], [137.0, 973.0], [137.0, 1078.0], [109.0, 1078.0]]], "lines": ["ああ．．．"]}, {"box": [848, 1234, 983, 1414], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[941.0, 1234.0], [983.0, 1234.0], [983.0, 1298.0], [941.0, 1298.0]], [[913.0, 1239.0], [940.0, 1239.0], [940.0, 1343.0], [913.0, 1343.0]], [[880.0, 1239.0], [907.0, 1239.0], [907.0, 1414.0], [880.0, 1414.0]], [[848.0, 1235.0], [880.0, 1235.0], [880.0, 1282.0], [848.0, 1282.0]]], "lines": ["ただ", "顔だけは", "捨てられなかっ", "た。"]}, {"box": [386, 1409, 445, 1577], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28, "lines_coords": [[[412.0, 1409.0], [445.0, 1409.0], [445.0, 1493.0], [412.0, 1493.0]], [[387.0, 1414.0], [409.0, 1414.0], [409.0, 1573.0], [387.0, 1573.0]]], "lines": ["そりゃ", "そうでしょう。"]}, {"box": [32,